OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable cloud, and some sunny
OL,6,Fspells for much of the day. Winds will
OL,7,Fremain light, and it will be feeling
OL,8,Fwarm in any sunny spells. Perhaps a
OL,9,Ffew showers spreading south into the
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers, perhaps heavy at
OL,13,Ffirst, before easing away south around
OL,14,Fmidnight. Low cloud, mist and the odd
OL,15,Fspot of drizzle then spreading south
OL,16,Fand west. Less cold than recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
