OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy start with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof light rain for some, although these
OL,7,Feasing by the afternoon. Cooler than
OL,8,Frecently, especially in the easterly
OL,9,Fbreeze, but turning sunny from the
OL,10,Feast later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,13,Fwith plenty of warm sunshine Wednesday
OL,14,Fand Thursday, but tempered by strong
OL,15,Feast to southeast breezes. Sunny
OL,16,Fspells and lighter winds Friday, but
OL,17,Fperhaps also showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
